data.description: Holiday Lake is a hidden jewel in the rolling hills and piney woods of East Texas. Take a quiet road to this charming lake house, where your lake adventure begins. Enjoy morning coffee or a cool beverage at sunset on the back porch, with water views and bird's songs, or just go fishing in the stocked lake, off your pier or in your boat. Grill your catch on the deck and dine under the stars. Inside, you'll find an open concept living room/kitchen with peaceful lake views, and a wood burning stove for those cool winter evenings. One bedroom and one half bath are located downstairs with the primary bedroom and bath located upstairs. There's also a mud room with shower and an indoor utility room. Bring your family and pets, or enjoy quiet solitude here at serene Holiday Lake. Measurements approx.
